sequenceDiagram
    participant Creator
    participant Validator as Manifest Validator
    participant Approver as Organization Approver
    participant Install as Installation Service
    participant DB as Installation and Permission Snapshot
    participant Host as Host Adapter or Runtime API
    participant Policy as Runtime Policy

    Creator->>Validator: Declare allowlisted permissions and entry points
    Validator-->>Creator: Valid or rejected
    Approver->>Install: Submit exact approved permission array
    Install->>Install: Verify install, compatibility, artifact, entitlement, kill switch
    Install->>DB: Persist active installation and snapshot
    Host->>Policy: Request operation, entry point, payload
    Policy->>DB: Read state and approved snapshot
    Policy->>Policy: Check operation, product type, path, permission, size, kill switch
    alt Policy allows
        Policy-->>Host: allowed, execution not_executed
    else Policy denies
        Policy-->>Host: denied with bounded reason
    end

